      "rationale": "Solver benchmarked against three analytical solutions: (1) Hagen-Poiseuille flow in a rotating reference frame, (2) lid-driven cavity at Re=1000 (Ghia et al. reference), and (3) Taylor-Couette flow for annular geometry. All benchmark comparisons within 0.5% of analytical solution. Code verification activities documented in verification report VR-2023-001."
