      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented in FDA pump benchmark protocol. All 15 validation experiments conducted within the declared operating envelope (flow 2–6 L/min, speed 2000–3500 RPM, hematocrit 30–45%). Test fluid: porcine blood with hematocrit adjusted to 33±1%. Temperature controlled at 36±0.5°C. Pump geometry fabricated to FDA benchmark drawings (dimensional inspection report on file). Test rig calibration certificates current (within 12 months of test date)."
