      "rationale": "At MRL 2 with medium model influence, separate numerical solver error assessment beyond code verification (already assessed) and discretization error (already assessed) is scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Iterative convergence residuals < 1e-6 confirmed for all production runs, and round-off error is negligible for double-precision arithmetic on the mesh sizes used. No additional assessment required at this risk level."
    },
    {
