      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/morrison/criteria/use-error-scopeout",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2 with medium model influence, formal use-error assessment is scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Simulation workflows are executed by a single trained analyst with 8 years of CFD experience in cardiovascular applications. Simulation setup checklists and peer review of boundary condition assignments are documented in the project quality plan. Independent review of input files performed by a second analyst prior to production runs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
