      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal model-form uncertainty assessment is scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model has been applied in multiple published FDA pump benchmark studies and is the accepted standard for this device class. Turbulence model sensitivity (SST k-ω vs. RSM) was evaluated as part of the uncertainty quantification, contributing ±3.2% to the total uncertainty budget, which is captured in the validation uncertainty estimates."
    },
    {
